msg: Added option for relative URLs to UuidToUrlTransformer

author: kelvingoodson
msg: The problem was that getAllStructuralFeatures was being called early while metadata construction was not yet complete,
and the structural features are cached in that call and not refreshed.  The fix uses an alternative and semantically more accurate tests which avoids the caching.
